1.0.name: wordpress/simple-ajax-contact-form
1.0.description:
Simple Ajax Contact Form is designed for Wordpress plugin. This multilingual contact form is easy to configure, you can create custom error messages, disable input fileds and create a custom captcha. Support

FEATURES * Custom error and success messages. * No page reloads. * Customizable captcha (Font type, color, size). * Color picker to edit captcha * jQuery Phone Mask (999) 999-9999

Translate

  • Spanish (es_ES) (H3 Fuzion)
  • Spanish Peru (es_PE) (H3 Fuzion)
  • Norwegian (nb_NO) Thanks to Gorm Naess
  • Russian (ru_RU) Thanks to Shlepakov
  • French (fr_FR) Thanks to Geoffrey Lovinfosse
  • Greek (el_EL) Thanks to Manos Mavrikakis
